# IMPORT DATA 2.0 – AI CATALOG INGESTION & SUPPLIER ONBOARDING CENTER

## Objective

Transform the current upload screen from a simple file uploader into a complete AI-powered supplier catalog onboarding workflow.

The user should be able to upload a supplier catalog and immediately understand:

- Which products already exist
- Which products are new
- Which products have pricing changes
- Which products have stock changes
- Which products are missing documentation
- Which products require manual review
- Which products can be synchronized with Zoho Books
- Which products should be added to Atlas Catalog

The experience must be optimized for both desktop and mobile.

